        <Parent_String>incandescent lamps (lighting device components) [300180294], electric lamps (lighting device components) [300037640], light bulbs [300037663], lighting device components [300037653], furnishings components [300241953], components by specific context [300241584], components (objects parts) [300241583], Components (hierarchy name) [300241490], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
